Displays up to 360Hz or QHD 240Hz increase gaming speed while MSI’s Cooler Boost 5 technology keeps the system running smoothly.

This video with guide you through the features, hidden tricks, and also how to use these products. Enjoy!
#MSI #MSIGaming #GEseries #MSILaptopTutorial
